ControllerBasedTabs
===================

This plugin extends the Widgets Tabnav to allow for the controllers to specify a tabnav using
syntax similar to the specification of a layout, e.g. 

controller_based_tabs "my_tabnav" 

The plugin will then set an instance variable, @controller_tabs that will be available in the 
view, like so:

<% tabnav @controller_tabs  do %>
	<div id="container" >
  	<%= yield :layout %>
	</div>
<% end %>

It will use a default called 'application_default_tabnav' if no tabnav is provided

 